platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 脳を刺激する目の錯覚パズル

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 箱の角度を動かし世界をつなぐ

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love how Moncage’s puzzles show the importance of seeing things from different perspectives. The storytelling vignettes packed into the faces of a rotating cube connect and combine in ever-evolving, surprising ways, and the challenge of making those connections sparks creativity and renders the impossible suddenly possible. Rarely has the concept of thinking outside the box been illustrated so well.
